cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use signalbench or the In-Band Signal Compliance (IBSC) metric, please cite this repository."
title: "In-Band Signal Compliance (IBSC) / signalbench"
abstract: >-
  A benchmark and a single metric (Signal-Response Correctness) that unify
  over-compliance (prompt injection) and under-compliance (temporal blindness,
  access-deny, memory-label, bot-policy) for LLM agents into one leaderboard.
  Includes the zero-dependency signalbench harness, an action-based grader,
  results for six frontier models plus a Claude Code deployed-agent contrast,
  and the raw per-item responses.
type: software
